      "rationale": "Validation testing used the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design, same titanium alloy, same ASTM F1717 test configuration, and same QoIs as the COU. The FEA model ensemble validated here is the same framework applied in the regulatory submission context. No domain extrapolation is required. Gradation 3 achieved."
